data.title: 624 W Remington Dr, Sunnyvale, CA 94087
data.meta_description: Brand new mid-century modern remodel from top to bottom with ~$200K in upgrades. Be the first to enjoy this revitalized, centrally-located, Sunnyvale Eichler home in one of the most sought after neighborhoods, 1 mile or less from local public and private schools, major parks, as well as numerous shopping & dining options. This home checks ALL the boxes – true Eichler with floor-to-ceiling windows creating an abundance of natural light throughout, large & private open-air atrium, updated chef’s kitchen with full breakfast bar, quartz countertops, shaker cabinets w/ under cabinet lighting, stainless steel appliances, open plan kitchen and family room overlooking both the atrium and the designer-inspired back landscape, separate living room and dining area, primary suite with full bath, walk-in closet, and private patio access, fully updated bathrooms throughout, spacious guest bedrooms, dual pane windows and sliders, new wide plank luxury vinyl floors throughout, well-manicured landscaping providing a sense of tranquility all around, extended 2-car carport + attached single garage. Premiere LOCATION! Less than 1 mile to top-rated public & private schools as well as parks and shopping centers. Just under 2 miles to Sunnyvale’s vibrant Downtown. Convenient commute to the Silicon Valley’s most renown Corporate campuses, including Apple, Microsoft, Amazon, LinkedIn, Synopsys, Symantec, Yahoo, NASA, Lockheed, NVIDIA, Google, Hewlett Packard, Cisco, eBay, Netflix, Meta, Adobe, Tesla, and many more. Access to several international airports with San Jose International Airport less than 10 miles away. Experience this move-in ready mid-century home in a prime Sunnyvale neighborhood.
